            "type": "ndarray",
            "desc_blocks": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "For NumPy >= 1.10.0, if `a` is an ndarray, then a view of `a` is\nreturned; otherwise a new array is created. For earlier NumPy\nversions a view of `a` is returned only if the order of the\naxes is changed, otherwise the input array is returned."
              }
            ]
          }
